### 查询课程教师列表
GET http://localhost:8080/course-teacher/list/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 添加课程教师
POST http://localhost:8080/course-teacher
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "name": "测试教师",
  "position": "讲师",
  "description": "测试教师简介"
}

### 修改课程教师
POST http://localhost:8080/course-teacher
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "courseId": 1,
  "name": "测试教师",
  "position": "高级讲师",
  "description": "修改后的简介"
}

### 删除课程教师
DELETE http://localhost:8080/course-teacher/1/1
Content-Type: application/json 